ustgesch\u00e4ft mit Potenzial - WELT |website=Welt.de |date=14 February 2016 |accessdate=9 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.gruenderszene.de/news/strafbefehl-lieferheld |title=Was steckt hinter dem Lieferheld-Strafbefehl? &#124; Gr\u00fcnderszene |website=Gruenderszene.de |date=10 January 2013 |accessdate=9 March 2017}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website}}\n\n{{Online food ordering}}\n{{MDAX companies}}\n\n[[Category:Online food ordering]]\n[[Category:Online retailers of Germany]]\n[[Category:Companies based in Berlin]]\n[[Category:Retail companies established in 2011]]\n[[Category:Internet properties established in 2011]]\n[[Category:German companies established in 2011]]\n[[Category:2017 initial public offerings]]\n[[Category:Companies listed on the Frankfurt Stock Exchange]]\n", "name_user": "Shivammehta24", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eHistory", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delivery_Hero"}
